screen_desc: The screenshot shows a sign-in page with options to sign in using Google or Facebook. There is also an option to sign in with a phone number by selecting the country code and entering the phone number. Alternatively, users can choose to use their email instead. A red "Continue" button is present for proceeding with the sign-in process. A note at the bottom mentions that a one-time verification code may be sent via text message to the associated phone number, and that message and data rates may apply.
